title: TomTom 7 for Windows Mobile (Rip from HTC Diamond)
description:
This is a cab installer for TomTom 7. This build is ripped from the HTC Diamond.

This doesn&#039;t include voices and maps. One map of local city can be downloaded for free and voices can also be downloaded via activesync connection on device itself. 

Just copy the CAB to the Windows Mobile device and run it.

Tested on Diamond and TyTN II with succes !

Cheers!
